Highlight:

  • The simple desk features a simple black and generous design can be perfectly integrated with any furniture in the home without being obtrusive.

  • Item dimession:
  • product size: 40*40*51.5cm
  • package dimession:52*42*7.5cm

Product features:

  • Our tea desk has double layers of storage that allow you to store for books, plant pots, snacks, fruit, coffee and so on,which can reduce clutter and make your home more tidy.
  • The metal round side table comes in classic coating, making it rustproof, antiwater.
  • This round table is conveinent to maintenance and clean. No fear of any food coffee drink stains, a light wipe with a rag can make it a new look.
  • The x-shaped leg structure of this coffee desk let the whole table more stable and not easy to shake
  • Our folding sofa side table is very easy to install, you can easily complete the assembe within 1 minute. Just spread the leg and then put the tray on it.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
